{"tid":669067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"封殺中國在美敏感投資 美國國會立法擴審查權","createTime":"2018-05-18T07:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T07:26:53.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b59d4b45f6b859a0ef96c9972a9cf2185495a888","tid":669067,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"美國參院銀行委員會和眾院金融服務委員會經過一年多商談，即將通過一項擴大「外國在美投資委員會」(CFIUS)權限和資源的法案，這項法案旨在封殺中國對美國投資的敏感交易，預計今年將成為法律。<br />\n<br />\nCFIUS作為跨政府部門的機構，將審查外國對美國企業的收購，可建議總統以國家安全為由封殺外國的收購案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12108/3149383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F12108%2F3149383&d=4aislN5SURMOPut2E0JZv8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=b1bf878c\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/12108/3149383</a>"},{"pid":"d4802f5817672508d8f571d35d33c455ce685917","tid":669067,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"唔係已經有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}